lead_paragraph: Kemba Walker scored 30 points and Cody Zeller had 15 to lead the Charlotte Hornets to a 119-99 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Kemba Walker Keeps Hornets Rolling in 119-99 Win Over 76ers
